&nbsp;


Selected participants (Allison Moore, Darsha Hewitt, Katherine Kline, Louisa Sage, Risa Hatayama) completed a series of workshops based on open source tools for artists including The GIMP, Blender 3D, Ardour and PureData, all while learning to maneuver though the Linux operating system. They present the result of the work.

